reviewText: Excellent DVD helps you understand the Canon 7D, so you can get outside and use the camera.
reviewing as I type, and it does appear to cover all the basics... if it fans out will consider the advance video which is the on I was going to get

This is a wonderful new camera.  But, make no doubt about it - a user manual of more than 500 pages in length will challenge even  the more experienced photographers.
Fortunately this DVD put that difficult to understand CANON PRODUCED manual and provided a very succinct learning aide that will very likely help you master your  new camera in no time at all.
